cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper deals with hyperspectral image classification, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also proposes a novel regularization strategy to improve the low-rank representation, which involves machine learning techniques. Hence, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories. The paper also deals with image processing and analysis, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
